      "default": "<p>Welcome to Rare Biblio, the premier destination for bibliophiles and book lovers who<br>appreciate the art of bookmaking.</p>",
      "info": "Use Shift+Enter after who for a line break, or edit HTML (e.g. br tag)."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
